# Expected serial output patterns for HobbyOS boot.
# Each non-empty, non-comment line is checked as a literal substring.
HobbyOS: Serial debug output initialized
GDT initialized
PIC remapped
IDT initialized
Interrupt handlers registered
PIT initialized at 100Hz
Keyboard initialized
PMM:
VMM initialized
Kernel heap initialized
Process subsystem initialized
Scheduler initialized
VFS initialized
RAMFS mounted
Interrupts enabled
